WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:03.400
Quorum — the Nonprofit Board OS.

00:03.560 --> 00:11.600
Welcome. This is Quorum — your board's private portal.
It's the one place where everything about launching your foundation lives.

00:11.780 --> 00:13.600
Let's take a quick look around.

00:13.770 --> 00:21.500
When you sign in, you land on your Dashboard. It greets you by name,
and shows, at a glance, how the launch is going.

00:21.680 --> 00:28.000
Down the left side is your menu. Everything in the portal
lives here, in seven simple sections.

00:28.200 --> 00:34.450
Documents holds your bylaws, minutes, and letters —
ready to sign online, no printer needed.

00:34.630 --> 00:41.600
The Launch Checklist walks you step by step, from
"we have an idea" to "we're an official charity."

00:41.780 --> 00:46.200
Board Votes is where the board makes decisions —
even between meetings.

00:46.360 --> 00:51.400
The Calendar keeps every board date in one place,
with one-click video calls.

00:51.580 --> 00:54.100
Notes is your own private notebook.

00:54.270 --> 00:58.700
And Team & Access shows who's on the board, and who can sign.

00:58.840 --> 01:09.100
Here's the good news: you don't need to learn it all today.
The portal always shows you the next step — and we'll walk through
each section together, one short video at a time.

01:09.220 --> 01:11.700
Ready? Let's start with signing in.
